{"tid":1469954,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［集思廣益］遇到鬼要點算","createTime":"2019-08-14T03:41:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T05:06:13.000Z","uid":144497,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"def27990702ccf1a135988e253997b1f88073f2d","tid":1469954,"uid":144497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:41:53.000Z","msg":"事先聲明︰<br />\n以下全由<span style=\"color: gold;\">和理非</span><span style=\"color: teal;\">冷氣軍師</span>建議，可能唔實際<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n歡迎提出意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">前題︰</span><br />\n做咗啲好鬼嘅嘢（主動打人、打記者、打救護<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />、可疑影相<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />），或者服裝上好鬼（戴耳機<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />、身上有明顯識別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />），先好懷疑係鬼<br />\n<ins>不過服裝上鬼都唔好做嘢住，等佢做嘢先</ins><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">一、打人、撞人等肢體碰撞</span><br />\n拍片同救人，被打時還手，搞掂就送佢走<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，當佢黐線佬<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">二、撩是鬥非</span><br />\n唔使理佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，當佢黐線佬<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">三、好可疑噉影相</span><br />\n遮樣遮耳<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，盡快走開<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，當佢黐線佬<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">四、發現藍衫／白衫</span><br />\n影相，笠落佢到，送佢走<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，當佢黐線佬<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">五、發現武器</span><br />\n影相，送佢到狗面前<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，屈佢係要攻擊狗狗嘅暴徒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，當佢黐線佬<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">或者</span><br />\n影相，<del>まばうどい</del><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，當佢重度黐線佬<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">總結︰</span><br />\n發現疑似係鬼但係乜都冇做就<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">完全唔理</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n否則<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一律當黐線佬噉處理</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n相信手足喺呢方面多少都有啲經驗，香港咁多黐線佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n重申歡迎大家畀意見獻計<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Let's think.<br />\n毋忘 612 721 811</span>"},{"pid":"789f2d3dc24f817301f4e8f67fa72c717fed149c","tid":1469954,"uid":25882,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:42:47.000Z","msg":"（長文）仲記唔記得咩叫兄弟爬山同不割𥱊<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1469926\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1469926</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3d39661785027fe7fd4a454b32343edc943f67d4","tid":1469954,"uid":144497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:46:10.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"ff5084b96a61e4c9fa29668e58f63b7eb039776e","tid":1469954,"uid":228830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:48:09.000Z","msg":"要佢大大聲大叫：<br />\n「中共滅亡！結束一黨專政。共產黨無好死。」"},{"pid":"a2d24ef9fa4f1d7ad2f0a05493aba4a5a309da75","tid":1469954,"uid":70884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:48:39.000Z","msg":"其實尋日處理得好好，好克制 <br />\n要盡量控制情緒，控制身邊人嘅情緒，不過打咗都唔割"},{"pid":"ee9621f807976106a9782deb201e052ea1097724","tid":1469954,"uid":144497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"789f2d3dc